    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It's in solid, well-loved shape and runs like a dream. It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle that still looks and feels great on the road. I\u2019ve taken care of the maintenance, and I\u2019d love to see it go to a good home. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
