      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example featuring the high-revving S54 straight-six, complete with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventive maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement. The suspension geometry is tight, utilizing Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings for optimal lateral grip. While the exterior shows minor road patina, the powertrain remains robust and the chassis is structurally excellent. A visceral, analog driving experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
